10. Links to Other Sites
Our Service may contain links to external sites not operated by us. We have no control over and assume no responsibility for the content or privacy practices of any third-party sites.
11. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of changes by updating the “Last Updated” date at the top of this Privacy Policy.
We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.
12. Contact Us
